# Template for the `.secrets` file act reads with --secret-file .secrets.
# Copy to .secrets (gitignored) and edit if needed.
#
# All OpenCHAMI images referenced by the workflow are public on GHCR, so
# a placeholder GITHUB_TOKEN value is sufficient to satisfy
# docker/login-action's input requirement. Replace with a real PAT only
# if you need to pull private images.
GITHUB_TOKEN=placeholder
